review:
A game forgotten by the developer!
1. Lack of anti-cheat 10 out of 10 farming bots;
2. A simulator about players killing 10 out of 10 farmbots in 360 head shots;
3. The buggy system displays items from the player if you've met him, of course, 10 out of 10 farm bots;
4. The update is equal to the new bug 10 out of 10 phar bots;
5. A wide selection of bots that will rape you 10 out of 10 farm bots.
We have a wonderful simulator game with bots, forget what a team shooter is, it doesn't even smell like it! 100 out of 10 farm bots!
